{"tid":2369924,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟呢個地球上有冇人可以同時用完洗頭水同護髮素？","createTime":"2021-01-17T14:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T04:08:03.000Z","uid":352372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2f43847951f5af43cd965892d86b28b56a826f","tid":2369924,"uid":352372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:39:03.000Z","msg":"男人老狗有時急起上嚟 用完洗頭水就唔用護髮素<br />\n最後搞到成支洗頭水用晒 護髮素仲有一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係買返嚟又係孖裝 用住A洗頭水加B護髮素個感覺好怪<br />\n有一期特登洗頭水同護髮素每次都唧一下 最後都係唔可以一齊用曬<br />\n究竟係得我係咁定係好多人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0ad07fafe6b51ca7ad841adeeb82bbc2dee7fc","tid":2369924,"uid":51900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"你唔買孖裝咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577fb048c7b655939723048f281fe857baabbf8a","tid":2369924,"uid":337336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"都係差唔多，用左好過冇用，又可以慳返一次水沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d19b7a352ab22ef0b121f675929cd0df562f72","tid":2369924,"uid":95158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T04:08:03.000Z","msg":"護髮素正確用法其實係要沖完洗頭水，之後印乾少少頭髮，再搽啲護髮素喺頭髮中段至尾段一兩分鐘，等啲頭髮吸收到護髮素嘅油份，輕輕再沖水。<br />\n<br />\n如果將護髮素搽埋根部封鎖咗髮根生長咁就會好快禿頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，男女都係咁話"}]}